0:05:04.16,000 --> 0:05:07,000
There we go.

106
0:05:07.16,000 --> 0:05:09,000
But I do think that perhaps design

107
0:05:09.16,000 --> 0:05:11,000
is getting big again.

108
0:05:11.16,000 --> 0:05:14,000
And that's happening through

109
0:05:14.16,000 --> 0:05:16,000
the application of design thinking

